  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improvement of the accessibility &amp; quality of education
School: Sarita Colonia school in Sarita Colonia 
1000 children, 50 teachers, parents
STAR - escuela
1: Reducci&#xF3;n de la pobreza (siguiendo el modelo de STAR-escuela)
1.	Birth certificates for approximately 1000 children.
2.	Development of state school into a STAR school: help 150-200 children with better education and 6 teachers with better skills.
3.	Training of 25-50 teachers in dynamics, fun math and technical reading. 
4.	Help 40-60 children with significant educational deficits at preschool.
5.	All children involved in one of our programs, their parents and their teachers benefit from our early stimulation program.
2: Desarrollo capacidades
School boards trained on management of schools
3: Cabildeo y soporte activo
Relations established with DRE, Reniec, Vaso de Leche, SIS.
Campaigning via Radio &amp; TV, local authorities

